5️⃣ IMMUTABILITY RULES
5.1 Structural Fields (Locked After Assignment)
Cannot edit if question used in any assigned run:
    • UniqueKey
    • Difficulty
    • Marks
    • NegativeMarks
    • QuestionType
    • QuestionImageFile
    • CorrectAnswer
    • Exam
    • Subject
UI shows lock icon with tooltip:
“Locked: Used in assigned test.”

5.2 Flexible Fields (Editable with Warning)
Editable even if used:
    • SolutionImageFile
    • TutorialVideoLink
    • SimulationLink
    • PrimaryTag
    • SecondaryTag
    • AdditionalTag
    • Topic
    • InternalNotes
Show warning:
“Changes affect future solution view only. Past scoring unaffected.”

6️⃣ VERSIONING MODEL
If structural change required:
System must:
    1. Duplicate question
    2. Increment version
    3. Generate new internal ID
    4. Mark old as deprecated
    5. Prevent new templates from using deprecated version (optional toggle)
Never mutate question used in completed run.
Each run stores:
questionVersionId
Ensures 10-year audit integrity.

7️⃣ DISTRIBUTION OVERVIEW
Displays:
L0
    • Global difficulty distribution
    • Chapter coverage heatmap
    • Marks distribution chart
L2 Adds
    • Overstay frequency per difficulty
    • Guess rate per difficulty
    • Risk impact per chapter
    • Discipline stress per chapter
All derived from questionAnalytics collection.

8️⃣ VALIDATION LOGS
Store:
institutes/{id}/questionUploadLogs/{uploadId}
Fields:
    • uploadedBy
    • timestamp
    • totalRows
    • errors
    • warnings
    • versionCreated
Logs immutable.
Rollback allowed only if:
    • Questions unused in any assigned template.

9️⃣ TAG MANAGEMENT
Tag operations allowed:
    • Create
    • Rename
    • Merge
    • Deprecate
Cannot delete tag if used in active template.
Tag updates affect:
    • Future analytics
    • Not historical run snapshots
No retroactive recalculation.

🔟 QUESTION ANALYTICS
Stored separately:
questionAnalytics/{questionId}
Contains:
    • avgRawPercentWhenUsed
    • avgAccuracyWhenUsed
    • guessRate
    • overstayRate
    • riskImpactScore
    • disciplineStressIndex
Updated on session submission.
Never calculated on read.

1️⃣1️⃣ HOT–WARM–COLD MODEL
HOT
Questions used current year.
WARM
Unused recently but active.
COLD
Unused > 2 years.
Images moved to archive storage bucket.
Metadata retained.
Never delete questions tied to historical runs.

1️⃣2️⃣ SECURITY RULES
    • Students cannot query questionBank.
    • Question editing disabled if assigned.
    • Versioning enforced server-side.
    • Upload requires admin role.

1️⃣3️⃣ PERFORMANCE RULES
Never:
    • Load full image in table view
    • Query without filter
    • Recompute distributions on page load
Always:
    • Use indexed filters
    • Paginate library
    • Precompute questionAnalytics
    • Lazy-load image preview

